ygData.messageBody:
In a group or solo?

I've avoided Sol B for the most part since I've heard nothing but horror
stories about the overcrowding there. Went there last week for the first
time and did pretty well. It was late at night so we didn't have to compete
with other groups for spawns.

Galtin
